---
title: Aubergine Parmigiana Style Traybake with Roasted Potatoes and Baby Leaves
description: Parmigiana is an Italian dish made with roasted or fried aubergine layered with tomato sauce and cheese before being baked. Our Aubergine Parmigiana Style Traybake is a simpler version, but still full of flavour.
